title: Sunsets
text: I like sunsets. I like clouds. I like sunsets with pretty clouds. These were all taken by me, with my limited photography equipment and skills (iPhone and a DJI drone).

title: Home
text: Hello there! Welcome to my corner of the internet, where I try post cool stuff I find in my life, opinions, thoughts, and some stuff that interests me. With my belief in free and open-source, all of the contents on this website are licensed under the MIT license unless otherwise stated.

title: Home
text:
About
I’m usually a person who stays silent, and observes. I like thinking about big questions and trying to understand the world. When I’m not silently daydreaming, I like to study advanced physics and mathematics on my own, as well as tinkering with technology and hardware.
If you’d describe me with one word, it’d probably be “nerd.” Other than nerd behavior, I like playing the string bass and piano, as well as watching sunsets and taking walks. I love identifying wild native plants in the area while hiking as well.
